text: Kazbek Kubadiyevich Zankishiev (; born 23 May 1992) is a Russian judoka.IJF profile He is the 2017 European bronze medalist in the 100 kg division. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1992 births Category:Russian male judoka Category:Living people Category:European Games competitors for Russia Category:Judoka at the 2019 European Games Category:European Games medalists in judo Category:European Games gold medalists for Russia
